sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant UI as UI
    participant BG as BackgroundTask
    participant API as GitHub API

    User->>UI: Tap "Send" on new conversation
    UI->>BG: Initiate POST request
    BG->>API: POST /pulls/:num/comments
    Note over API: Network hang / no response
    loop Infinite Wait
        BG--xAPI: No response
        UI->>User: Spinner (no timeout/error)
    end
    User->>UI: Force close app
    Note over UI: Volatile RAM cleared -> comment lost on many devices
